    <content>
      <![CDATA[<div class="post-brief">  <div><b>项目类型</b><span>嵌入式视觉 / 巡检装置</span></div>  <div><b>核心技术</b><span>OpenMV, LAB 阈值, UART, MPU6050</span></div>  <div><b>当前状态</b><span>算法与工程结构已整理，适合继续补 demo 视频</span></div></div><h2 id="项目概述"><a href="#项目概述" class="headerlink" title="项目概述"></a>项目概述</h2><p>本项目是一个 <strong>绳驱巡检装置</strong> 的视觉子系统，基于 OpenMV Cam 实现。参赛装置通过绳索悬挂运动，OpenMV 负责识别地面上的橙色圆点标记，为控制板提供末端精确定位修正，并在巡检过程中检测火源。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">openmv_inspection/</span><br><span class="line">├── main.py              # 主循环：图像采集、模式调度、串口收发</span><br><span class="line">├── config.py            # 全局配置（颜色阈值、模式定义、硬件参数）</span><br><span class="line">├── runtime_config.py    # 运行时配置覆盖</span><br><span class="line">├── pose.py              # 定位核心：首圆绑定 + 目标坐标换算</span><br><span class="line">├── tracking.py          # 追踪逻辑：橙色 blob 锁定 + 到达判定</span><br><span class="line">├── fire.py              # 火源检测与去重</span><br><span class="line">├── mpu6050.py           # MPU6050 姿态读取与低通滤波</span><br><span class="line">├── uart_comm.py         # UART 协议封装（命令解析 + 数据上报）</span><br><span class="line">├── 算法详解.md           # 全部算法逐文件中文详解</span><br><span class="line">└── 项目功能解释.md        # 项目逻辑与设计思路</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="系统架构"><a href="#系统架构" class="headerlink" title="系统架构"></a>系统架构</h2><h3 id="硬件组成"><a href="#硬件组成" class="headerlink" title="硬件组成"></a>硬件组成</h3><table><thead><tr><th>组件</th><th>型号</th><th>作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>摄像头</td><td>OpenMV Cam</td><td>图像采集与视觉处理</td></tr><tr><td>下位机</td><td>自制控制板</td><td>电机驱动与运动控制</td></tr><tr><td>IMU</td><td>MPU6050</td><td>姿态监测（俯仰&#x2F;横滚）</td></tr><tr><td>通信</td><td>UART @ 460800bps</td><td>OpenMV ↔ 控制板 双向通信</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="工作模式"><a href="#工作模式" class="headerlink" title="工作模式"></a>工作模式</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">MODE_IDLE   = 0   空闲</span><br><span class="line">MODE_HOME   = 1   回原点（回到中心圆 0）</span><br><span class="line">MODE_PATROL = 2   自动巡检（按序遍历各目标点）</span><br><span class="line">MODE_MANUAL = 3   手动指定（控制板指定目标圆索引）</span><br><span class="line">MODE_SNAKE  = 4   蛇形巡检（带火源检测的巡检模式）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="定位方案：”控制板粗定位-OpenMV-精修”"><a href="#定位方案：”控制板粗定位-OpenMV-精修”" class="headerlink" title="定位方案：”控制板粗定位 + OpenMV 精修”"></a>定位方案：”控制板粗定位 + OpenMV 精修”</h3><p>控制板负责将装置粗略移动到目标圆附近，OpenMV 负责末端视觉精修：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 控制板 → 粗移模块到目标圆附近</span><br><span class="line">2. OpenMV → 识别视野中橙色圆 blob</span><br><span class="line">3. OpenMV → 计算 blob 中心与图像中心的像素偏差</span><br><span class="line">4. OpenMV → 利用圆直径估算比例尺 (px/cm)</span><br><span class="line">5. OpenMV → 反推模块当前位置，上报偏移量</span><br><span class="line">6. 控制板 → 执行最后精调，完成入圆</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="核心算法"><a href="#核心算法" class="headerlink" title="核心算法"></a>核心算法</h2><h3 id="1-橙色目标识别与追踪"><a href="#1-橙色目标识别与追踪" class="headerlink" title="1. 橙色目标识别与追踪"></a>1. 橙色目标识别与追踪</h3><p>通过 LAB 颜色阈值分割提取橙色圆点，配合多级筛选逻辑：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 多组阈值适应不同光照</span></span><br><span class="line">ORANGE_THRESHOLDS = [</span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">46</span>, <span class="number">29</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">55</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">56</span>),      <span class="comment"># 标准</span></span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">79</span>, <span class="number">92</span>, <span class="number">14</span>, -<span class="number">53</span>, <span class="number">127</span>, <span class="number">15</span>),  <span class="comment"># 弱光</span></span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">25</span>, <span class="number">95</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">70</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">127</span>),     <span class="comment"># 过曝</span></span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">15</span>, <span class="number">80</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">80</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">95</span>),      <span class="comment"># 红光干扰</span></span><br><span class="line">    (<span class="number">55</span>, <span class="number">100</span>, -<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">60</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">127</span>), <span class="comment"># 备用</span></span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>PatrolTargetLock</code> 类实现了断线重锁：当目标短暂丢失时，基于最近位置预测和最大跳变距离容忍，在 2 帧内可自动重锁。</p><h3 id="2-控制确认门-TargetConfirmGate"><a href="#2-控制确认门-TargetConfirmGate" class="headerlink" title="2. 控制确认门 (TargetConfirmGate)"></a>2. 控制确认门 (TargetConfirmGate)</h3><p>防止抖动误触发到达信号：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">TargetConfirmGate</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, required_frames=<span class="number">3</span>, max_shift_px=<span class="number">18</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 连续 N 帧目标在阈值范围内 → 确认到达</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 任何一帧超出 max_shift_px → 重置计数器</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>连续 3 帧目标位置稳定，才判定为真正到达，有效防止电机抖动引起的误报。</p><h3 id="3-位置反推"><a href="#3-位置反推" class="headerlink" title="3. 位置反推"></a>3. 位置反推</h3><p>已知目标圆的世界坐标 <code>(tx, ty)</code> 和实测像素比例尺，从 blob 偏差反推当前位置：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dx_cm = (blob.cx - 160) / pixels_per_cm</span><br><span class="line">dy_cm = (120 - blob.cy) / pixels_per_cm</span><br><span class="line">xc = tx - dx_cm</span><br><span class="line">yc = ty - dy_cm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-MPU6050-姿态监测"><a href="#4-MPU6050-姿态监测" class="headerlink" title="4. MPU6050 姿态监测"></a>4. MPU6050 姿态监测</h3><p>I2C 自动寻址，互补滤波融合加速度计与陀螺仪数据，实时监测装置俯仰和横滚角，确保运行姿态稳定。</p><h3 id="5-火源检测"><a href="#5-火源检测" class="headerlink" title="5. 火源检测"></a>5. 火源检测</h3><p>在 SNAKE 模式下，每帧额外检测红色&#x2F;橙色火源区域，发现后立即上报坐标并暂停运动，等待控制板处理。</p><h2 id="UART-通信协议"><a href="#UART-通信协议" class="headerlink" title="UART 通信协议"></a>UART 通信协议</h2><p>OpenMV 与控制板之间的双向协议：</p><table><thead><tr><th>方向</th><th>命令</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>控制板 → OpenMV</td><td><code>MODE</code>, <code>TARGET</code></td><td>模式切换、目标设定</td></tr><tr><td>OpenMV → 控制板</td><td><code>OFFSET</code></td><td>像素偏移量 (dx, dy)</td></tr><tr><td>OpenMV → 控制板</td><td><code>ARRIVED</code></td><td>到达目标点通知</td></tr><tr><td>OpenMV → 控制板</td><td><code>POSITION</code></td><td>当前世界坐标 (xc, yc)</td></tr><tr><td>OpenMV → 控制板</td><td><code>FIRE</code></td><td>火源坐标上报</td></tr><tr><td>OpenMV → 控制板</td><td><code>ANGLES</code></td><td>当前俯仰&#x2F;横滚角</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="项目特点"><a href="#项目特点" class="headerlink" title="项目特点"></a>项目特点</h2><ul><li><strong>全中文算法文档</strong> — <code>算法详解.md</code> 逐函数解释设计意图与优化理由，方便团队成员理解和维护</li><li><strong>生产级细节</strong> — LAB 阈值自动归一化（防写反）、欧氏距离平方代替开根号（嵌入式优化）、到达防抖确认</li><li><strong>双通道定位</strong> — 控制板粗定位 + 视觉精修，分担系统压力</li><li><strong>一键现场调试</strong> — IDE 实时叠加显示位置、模式、姿态、FPS，配合联调检查表快速排障</li></ul><p>该项目是 2026 年校赛”简易绳驱巡检装置”题目的视觉部分实现，完整实现了从橙色目标识别、位置解算、多模式巡检到火源检测的全部功能链路。</p>]]>
    </content>
