    <summary>基于 OpenMV 的绳驱巡检装置视觉子系统，包含橙色目标识别、视觉定位、串口通信和火源检测。</summary>
    <title>OpenMV 绳驱巡检装置视觉系统</title>
    <updated>2026-05-26T13:46:58.920Z</updated>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <author>
      <name>beid</name>
    </author>
    <category term="技术折腾" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/categories/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE/"/>
    <category term="嵌入式" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/tags/%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%BC%8F/"/>
    <category term="STM32" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/tags/STM32/"/>
    <category term="MSP430" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/tags/MSP430/"/>
    <category term="MCP" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/tags/MCP/"/>
    <category term="AI工具" scheme="https://yihang56666-sketch.github.io/tags/AI%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/"/>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<div class="post-brief">  <div><b>项目类型</b><span>AI 工具链 / 嵌入式开发辅助</span></div>  <div><b>核心技术</b><span>Python CLI, MCP, 芯片资料库, 自动化分析</span></div>  <div><b>价值</b><span>把重复的硬件资料查询和调试流程沉淀成工具能力</span></div></div><h2 id="项目概述"><a href="#项目概述" class="headerlink" title="项目概述"></a>项目概述</h2><p>这是一个面向嵌入式硬件工程师的 <strong>AI 辅助工具集</strong>，让 Claude Code 等 AI 编程助手能够理解芯片数据手册、开发板原理图，并提供外设配置、引脚分析、CubeMX 辅助等能力。项目包含三个部分：</p><ul><li><strong>chip skill</strong> — 核心 Python 工具，提供命令行接口</li><li><strong>chip-mcp</strong> — MCP 协议服务器，供 AI 工具直接调用</li><li><strong>硬件分析报告</strong> — 对 MSP430G2、STM32F407VET6 等芯片的深度分析文档</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">skill/</span><br><span class="line">├── chip/                    # 核心 skill</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── scripts/chip.py      # 主程序</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── configs/config.yaml  # 配置文件</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── resources/           # 数据库 (boards, chips, tasks)</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── skill.json           # Skill 描述</span><br><span class="line">│   └── requirements.txt     # Python 依赖</span><br><span class="line">├── chip-mcp/                # MCP 服务器</span><br><span class="line">│   ├── server.py            # MCP 协议服务端</span><br><span class="line">│   └── mcp.json             # MCP 配置</span><br><span class="line">├── 使用指南.md               # 用户文档</span><br><span class="line">└── 分析报告/示例项目          # 实际案例</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Chip-Skill-核心功能"><a href="#Chip-Skill-核心功能" class="headerlink" title="Chip Skill 核心功能"></a>Chip Skill 核心功能</h2><h3 id="1-芯片-板子搜索"><a href="#1-芯片-板子搜索" class="headerlink" title="1. 芯片&#x2F;板子搜索"></a>1. 芯片&#x2F;板子搜索</h3><p>通过命令行快速搜索芯片数据手册和开发板原理图：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py search STM32F103C8T6</span><br><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py schematic bluepill</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-硬件深度分析"><a href="#2-硬件深度分析" class="headerlink" title="2. 硬件深度分析"></a>2. 硬件深度分析</h3><p>对开发板进行全面的硬件特性分析，包括处理器架构、存储器、外设资源、引脚分配等。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py analyze bluepill</span><br><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py pinout STM32F103C8T6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-外设使用指南"><a href="#3-外设使用指南" class="headerlink" title="3. 外设使用指南"></a>3. 外设使用指南</h3><p>提供 UART、I2C、SPI、ADC 等常见外设的配置指南：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py peripheral UART --chip STM32</span><br><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py peripheral I2C --chip STM32</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-CubeMX-配置辅助"><a href="#4-CubeMX-配置辅助" class="headerlink" title="4. CubeMX 配置辅助"></a>4. CubeMX 配置辅助</h3><p>生成 STM32CubeMX 项目配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py cubemx STM32F1 --project MyProject</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-任务解决方案"><a href="#5-任务解决方案" class="headerlink" title="5. 任务解决方案"></a>5. 任务解决方案</h3><p>为常见硬件任务提供完整的代码方案（LED 闪烁、UART 回显等）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py task blinky --board bluepill</span><br><span class="line">python scripts/chip.py task i2c-sensor --board bluepill</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="MCP-服务器"><a href="#MCP-服务器" class="headerlink" title="MCP 服务器"></a>MCP 服务器</h2><p><code>chip-mcp/server.py</code> 将 Chip Skill 包装为标准 MCP（Model Context Protocol）服务器，使得 Cline、Cursor 等 AI 编码工具可以直接调用其功能。MCP 协议定义的工具有：</p><table><thead><tr><th>工具名</th><th>功能</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>search_datasheet</code></td><td>搜索芯片数据手册</td></tr><tr><td><code>search_schematic</code></td><td>搜索板子原理图</td></tr><tr><td><code>analyze_board</code></td><td>分析板子硬件特性</td></tr><tr><td><code>cubemx_assist</code></td><td>CubeMX 配置辅助</td></tr><tr><td><code>pinout_analysis</code></td><td>引脚分配分析</td></tr><tr><td><code>peripheral_guide</code></td><td>外设使用指南</td></tr><tr><td><code>task_solution</code></td><td>硬件任务解决方案</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="硬件分析报告"><a href="#硬件分析报告" class="headerlink" title="硬件分析报告"></a>硬件分析报告</h2><p>项目中还包含两份深入的芯片分析报告：</p><h3 id="MSP430G2-LaunchPad"><a href="#MSP430G2-LaunchPad" class="headerlink" title="MSP430G2 LaunchPad"></a>MSP430G2 LaunchPad</h3><p>德州仪器 (TI) 的超低功耗入门级开发板：</p><ul><li><strong>MCU</strong>: MSP430G2553 (16位 RISC, 16MHz)</li><li><strong>存储</strong>: 16KB Flash, 512B RAM</li><li><strong>外设</strong>: 10位 ADC, 2×定时器, UART&#x2F;I2C&#x2F;SPI</li><li><strong>特色</strong>: 超低功耗（uA 级），适合电池供电应用</li></ul><h3 id="STM32F407VET6"><a href="#STM32F407VET6" class="headerlink" title="STM32F407VET6"></a>STM32F407VET6</h3><p>意法半导体高性能 Cortex-M4 微控制器：</p><ul><li><strong>CPU</strong>: ARM Cortex-M4 @168MHz, 单精度 FPU</li><li><strong>存储</strong>: 512KB Flash, 192KB SRAM</li><li><strong>外设</strong>: 3×12位 ADC, 2×DAC, DMA, USB OTG, 以太网</li><li><strong>特色</strong>: DSP 指令集，适合数字信号处理</li></ul><h2 id="SKILL-设计与集成"><a href="#SKILL-设计与集成" class="headerlink" title="SKILL 设计与集成"></a>SKILL 设计与集成</h2><p>该工具遵循 EmbeddedSkills 规范，通过 <code>skill.json</code> 声明元数据、触发词和使用示例：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;chip&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;capabilities&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;search_datasheet&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;搜索芯片数据手册&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;analyze_board&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;分析板子硬件特性&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;pinout_analysis&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;引脚分配分析&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;peripheral_guide&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;外设使用指南&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;triggers&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="string">&quot;chip&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;board&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;datasheet&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;stm32&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="string">&quot;原理图&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在 Claude Code 中安装后，可以直接通过 <code>/chip</code> 命令唤起：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/chip search stm32f103c8t6</span><br><span class="line">/chip analyze bluepill</span><br><span class="line">/chip cubemx stm32f4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>这个工具集的核心思路是：<strong>将硬件知识结构化，让 AI 能够理解和运用</strong>。传统嵌入式开发中，工程师需要反复查阅数据手册、原理图、外设参考手册，而通过这套工具，AI 助手可以在对话中直接获取这些信息并辅助开发——从选型分析、外设配置到代码生成，形成完整的辅助闭环。</p><p>项目基于 MIT 协议开源，支持自定义开发板数据库，方便团队接入自有硬件平台。</p>]]>
    </content>
