    <content>
      <![CDATA[<div class="post-brief">  <div><b>项目类型</b><span>计算机视觉 / 图像拼接</span></div>  <div><b>核心技术</b><span>SIFT, FLANN, RANSAC, Homography</span></div>  <div><b>输出结果</b><span>校园图像全景拼接和匹配过程可视化</span></div></div><h2 id="项目简介"><a href="#项目简介" class="headerlink" title="项目简介"></a>项目简介</h2><p>本项目实现了一个基于 <strong>SIFT + FLANN + RANSAC + Homography</strong> 的传统图像拼接（全景拼接）系统。以三张存在重叠区域的校园风景图作为输入，以中间帧为参考帧，将左右两张图变换投影到参考帧坐标系下，融合得到一张完整的全景图。</p><h2 id="实现流程"><a href="#实现流程" class="headerlink" title="实现流程"></a>实现流程</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">原始图像 → SIFT 特征提取 → FLANN 特征匹配 →</span><br><span class="line">Lowe&#x27;s 比值筛选 → RANSAC 估计单应矩阵 →</span><br><span class="line">透视变换 → 图像融合 → 裁剪输出全景图</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-SIFT-特征提取"><a href="#1-SIFT-特征提取" class="headerlink" title="1. SIFT 特征提取"></a>1. SIFT 特征提取</h3><p>对三张输入图像分别提取 SIFT（Scale-Invariant Feature Transform）特征点。SIFT 具有尺度不变性和旋转不变性，适用于存在视角差异的图像匹配场景。</p><p><img src="/images/stitching/kp_0023.jpg"><br><img src="/images/stitching/kp_0024.jpg"><br><img src="/images/stitching/kp_0025.jpg"><br><em>三张图像上的 SIFT 特征点可视化</em></p><h3 id="2-FLANN-特征匹配"><a href="#2-FLANN-特征匹配" class="headerlink" title="2. FLANN 特征匹配"></a>2. FLANN 特征匹配</h3><p>使用 FLANN（Fast Library for Approximate Nearest Neighbors）匹配器进行快速近似最近邻搜索，配合 <strong>Lowe’s 比值检验</strong>（阈值 0.7）筛选高质量匹配对，剔除模糊匹配。</p><p><img src="/images/stitching/match_1_2.jpg"><br><em>0023 ↔ 0024 特征匹配结果</em></p><p><img src="/images/stitching/match_3_2.jpg"><br><em>0025 ↔ 0024 特征匹配结果</em></p><h3 id="3-RANSAC-估计单应矩阵"><a href="#3-RANSAC-估计单应矩阵" class="headerlink" title="3. RANSAC 估计单应矩阵"></a>3. RANSAC 估计单应矩阵</h3><p>利用匹配好的特征点对，通过 <strong>RANSAC</strong>（随机抽样一致）算法鲁棒地估计图像间的单应变换矩阵（Homography），同时剔除误匹配点。</p><h3 id="4-图像映射与融合"><a href="#4-图像映射与融合" class="headerlink" title="4. 图像映射与融合"></a>4. 图像映射与融合</h3><p>以中间帧 <code>0024.jpg</code> 为参考坐标系，将左右两图通过单应矩阵变换投影到参考帧空间。采用<strong>直接覆盖融合</strong>策略（非零像素覆盖），最后自动裁剪黑边。</p><h2 id="核心代码"><a href="#核心代码" class="headerlink" title="核心代码"></a>核心代码</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> cv2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    img1 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">&#x27;0023.jpg&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    img2 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">&#x27;0024.jpg&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    img3 = cv2.imread(<span class="string">&#x27;0025.jpg&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    gray1 = cv2.cvtColor(img1, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)</span><br><span class="line">    gray2 = cv2.cvtColor(img2, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)</span><br><span class="line">    gray3 = cv2.cvtColor(img3, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 1. SIFT 特征提取</span></span><br><span class="line">    sift = cv2.SIFT_create()</span><br><span class="line">    kp1, des1 = sift.detectAndCompute(gray1, <span class="literal">None</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    kp2, des2 = sift.detectAndCompute(gray2, <span class="literal">None</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    kp3, des3 = sift.detectAndCompute(gray3, <span class="literal">None</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 2. FLANN 匹配 + Lowe&#x27;s 比值筛选</span></span><br><span class="line">    flann = cv2.FlannBasedMatcher(<span class="built_in">dict</span>(algorithm=<span class="number">1</span>, trees=<span class="number">5</span>), <span class="built_in">dict</span>(checks=<span class="number">50</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    matches12 = flann.knnMatch(des1, des2, k=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    matches32 = flann.knnMatch(des3, des2, k=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    good12 = [m <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> matches12 <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(m) == <span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> m[<span class="number">0</span>].distance &lt; <span class="number">0.7</span> * m[<span class="number">1</span>].distance]</span><br><span class="line">    good32 = [m <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> matches32 <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(m) == <span class="number">2</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> m[<span class="number">0</span>].distance &lt; <span class="number">0.7</span> * m[<span class="number">1</span>].distance]</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 3. RANSAC 估计单应矩阵</span></span><br><span class="line">    pts1 = np.float32([kp1[m.queryIdx].pt <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> good12]).reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    pts2_1 = np.float32([kp2[m.trainIdx].pt <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> good12]).reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    h1, _ = cv2.findHomography(pts1, pts2_1, cv2.RANSAC, <span class="number">5.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    pts3 = np.float32([kp3[m.queryIdx].pt <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> good32]).reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    pts2_3 = np.float32([kp2[m.trainIdx].pt <span class="keyword">for</span> m <span class="keyword">in</span> good32]).reshape(-<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    h3, _ = cv2.findHomography(pts3, pts2_3, cv2.RANSAC, <span class="number">5.0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 4. 透视变换 + 融合</span></span><br><span class="line">    h, w = img2.shape[:<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line">    t = np.array([[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, w], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="built_in">int</span>(h/<span class="number">2</span>)], [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>]], dtype=np.float32)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    result = cv2.warpPerspective(img1, t @ h1, (w * <span class="number">3</span>, h * <span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    res_right = cv2.warpPerspective(img3, t @ h3, (w * <span class="number">3</span>, h * <span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    res_center = cv2.warpPerspective(img2, t, (w * <span class="number">3</span>, h * <span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 非零像素覆盖融合</span></span><br><span class="line">    mask_right = np.<span class="built_in">any</span>(res_right &gt; <span class="number">0</span>, axis=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    result[mask_right] = res_right[mask_right]</span><br><span class="line">    mask_center = np.<span class="built_in">any</span>(res_center &gt; <span class="number">0</span>, axis=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    result[mask_center] = res_center[mask_center]</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 自动裁剪黑边</span></span><br><span class="line">    gray = cv2.cvtColor(result, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)</span><br><span class="line">    _, thresh = cv2.threshold(gray, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, cv2.THRESH_BINARY)</span><br><span class="line">    x, y, w_box, h_box = cv2.boundingRect(cv2.findNonZero(thresh))</span><br><span class="line">    cv2.imwrite(<span class="string">&quot;final_panorama.jpg&quot;</span>, result[y:y+h_box, x:x+w_box])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="拼接结果"><a href="#拼接结果" class="headerlink" title="拼接结果"></a>拼接结果</h2><p>最终的拼接效果相当自然，三张图像在重叠区域的对齐精度较高，接缝处过渡无明显断裂感。</p><p><img src="/images/stitching/final_panorama.jpg"></p><blockquote><p><strong>拼接参数</strong>：输入 3 × 576×384 → 输出 955×463</p></blockquote><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>本实践完整走通了传统图像拼接的经典流程：</p><table><thead><tr><th>步骤</th><th>方法</th><th>作用</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>特征提取</td><td>SIFT</td><td>尺度&#x2F;旋转不变的特征点检测</td></tr><tr><td>特征匹配</td><td>FLANN + Lowe’s 0.7</td><td>快速近似匹配 + 低质量筛除</td></tr><tr><td>变换估计</td><td>RANSAC + Homography</td><td>鲁棒估计透视变换关系</td></tr><tr><td>图像融合</td><td>直接覆盖 + 黑边裁剪</td><td>生成完整全景图</td></tr></tbody></table><p>这种基于特征的传统方法在纹理丰富、重叠度适中的场景下效果非常稳定，同时也是理解现代深度学习特征匹配方法（SuperPoint、SuperGlue 等）的重要基础。</p>]]>
    </content>
